      "strengths_deep_dive": [
        "BLOOM Charity excels in maximizing the utility of every dollar donated. By leveraging a volunteer-led model, they achieve a <cite id=\"8\">fundraising efficiency of $0.01 per $1 raised</cite>, which is significantly better than industry averages. Their financial health is further bolstered by <cite id=\"9\">21.3 months of working capital</cite>, ensuring that their 'Magical PlayGardens' and enrichment programs can continue even during funding fluctuations. This stability is paired with high accountability, evidenced by an <cite id=\"10\">overall score of 89.89.5/100 from Charity Navigator</cite>."
      ],
      "summary": "BLOOM Charity is a volunteer-led organization dedicated to improving the lives of at-risk children and orphans through play-based healing and crisis relief. Founded in <cite id=\"1\">2017</cite>, the charity focuses on creating 'Magical PlayGardens' and providing essential enrichment services in regions like Morocco and Palestine. The organization has demonstrated rapid <cite id=\"2\">early-stage growth</cite>, with revenue increasing from <cite id=\"3\">$107,186 in 2022 to $551,810 in 2024</cite>. Despite this growth, BLOOM maintains a lean operational model. They reported a <cite id=\"4\">98.7% program expense ratio</cite> in their most recent filings, ensuring that donor funds are directed toward direct services. Their work includes large-scale humanitarian efforts, such as providing <cite id=\"5\">700,000 meals in Gaza</cite> and building <cite id=\"6\">11 PlayGardens</cite> to support childhood development. The charity holds a <cite id=\"7\">Platinum Seal of Transparency from Candid</cite>, reflecting a high commitment to public disclosure and accountability.",
